AddressInfo.Title: ASDA Leyton Mills Superstore
AddressInfo.AccessComments: Points can be found 3 rows along to the left of the Asda shop entrance, rows nearest to the shop building. Look for round Electric Plug sign in Asda Green on a post by the bays.
